data.text:
Thank you for your interest in the Cathedral of St. John the Baptist. The Catholic Cathedral of the Diocese of Charleston.

Whether you are just visiting, looking for your spiritual home, returning to the Catholic Faith or are interested in finding out more about the Catholic Church, we are happy to have you here!

The Cathedral Parish is a place to deepen your Catholic faith and to use your gifts of time and talent as disciples of Christ.
